(function(){'use strict';function _skeletonRows(cols,rows){let html='';for(let r=0;r<rows;r++){html+='<tr>';for(let c=0;c<cols;c++)html+='<td><span class="skeleton-cell" style="width:60%"></span></td>';html+='</tr>';}return html;}let watchlistLoaded=false;async function fetchWatchlist(){const tbody=document.getElementById('watchlist-table-body');tbody.innerHTML=_skeletonRows(7,3);const res=await window.Common.csrfFetch('/api/watchlist');if(!res.ok){tbody.innerHTML='<tr><td colspan="7" class="text-center text-danger py-3">Ошибка загрузки</td></tr>';return;}const items=await res.json();watchlistLoaded=true;const esc=window.Common.escapeHtml;if(!items.length){tbody.innerHTML=`<tr><td colspan="7" class="text-center text-muted py-4">⭐ Список пуст. Добавьте облигации через кнопку «+Добавить».</td></tr>`;return;}tbody.innerHTML=items.map(item=>{const price=item.price !=null ? item.price.toFixed(2)+' ₽':'—';const ytm=item.ytm !=null ? item.ytm.toFixed(2)+' %':'—';const nkd=item.nkd !=null ? item.nkd.toFixed(2)+' ₽':'—';return `<tr><td>${esc(item.name)}</td><td><span class="isin-link" onclick="openBondChart('${esc(item.isin)}')">${esc(item.isin)}</span></td><td>${price}</td><td>${ytm}</td><td>${nkd}</td><td class="text-muted small">${esc(item.added_at)}</td><td><button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger" onclick="removeFromWatchlist('${esc(item.isin)}')">✕</button></td></tr>`;}).join('');}window.loadWatchlistIfNeeded=function(){if(!watchlistLoaded)fetchWatchlist();};window.addWatchlistDirect=async function(){const inputEl=document.getElementById('watchlistIsinInput');const isin=inputEl ? inputEl.value:null;if(!isin)return;const res=await window.Common.csrfFetch('/api/watchlist',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({isin:isin.trim().toUpperCase()}),});const data=await res.json();if(res.ok){window.Common.showToast(data.message);if(inputEl)inputEl.value='';watchlistLoaded=false;fetchWatchlist();}else{window.Common.showSystemMessage(data.message,true);}};window.removeFromWatchlist=async function(isin){window.Common.askConfirmation(`Удалить ${isin}из избранного?`,async()=>{const res=await window.Common.csrfFetch(`/api/watchlist/${isin}`,{method:'DELETE'});const data=await res.json();window.Common.showToast(data.message,!res.ok);watchlistLoaded=false;fetchWatchlist();});};window.runScreener=async function(){const tbody=document.getElementById('screener-table-body');const loading=document.getElementById('screener-loading');loading.style.display='block';tbody.innerHTML='';const params=new URLSearchParams();const ids={min_ytm:'screenerMinYtm',max_ytm:'screenerMaxYtm',maturity_from:'screenerMatFrom',maturity_to:'screenerMatTo',issuer_type:'screenerIssuerType',min_duration:'screenerMinDuration',max_duration:'screenerMaxDuration',};for(const[key,id]of Object.entries(ids)){const v=document.getElementById(id)?.value;if(v)params.set(key,v);}const res=await window.Common.csrfFetch('/api/screener?'+params.toString());loading.style.display='none';if(!res.ok){tbody.innerHTML='<tr><td colspan="6" class="text-danger text-center py-3">Ошибка загрузки</td></tr>';return;}const results=await res.json();const esc=window.Common.escapeHtml;if(!results.length){tbody.innerHTML='<tr><td colspan="6" class="text-center text-muted py-4">Ничего не найдено по заданным фильтрам.</td></tr>';return;}tbody.innerHTML=results.map(b=>{const ytm=b.ytm !=null ? b.ytm.toFixed(2)+' %':'—';const coupon=b.coupon !=null ? b.coupon+' ₽':'—';const mat=b.matdate || '—';return `<tr><td>${esc(b.name || b.secid)}</td><td><span class="isin-link" onclick="openBondChart('${esc(b.isin)}')">${esc(b.isin)}</span></td><td>${ytm}</td><td>${esc(mat)}</td><td>${coupon}</td><td><button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-success" title="Добавить в избранное" onclick="addScreenerToWatchlist('${esc(b.isin)}')">⭐</button></td></tr>`;}).join('');};window.clearScreener=function(){['screenerMinYtm','screenerMaxYtm','screenerMatFrom','screenerMatTo','screenerIssuerType','screenerMinDuration','screenerMaxDuration'].forEach(id=>{if(window.fpClear &&(id==='screenerMatFrom' || id==='screenerMatTo')){window.fpClear(id);return;}const el=document.getElementById(id);if(el)el.value='';});const tbody=document.getElementById('screener-table-body');tbody.innerHTML='<tr><td colspan="6" class="text-center text-muted py-4">Задайте фильтры и нажмите «Найти».</td></tr>';};window.addScreenerToWatchlist=async function(isin){const res=await window.Common.csrfFetch('/api/watchlist',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({isin}),});const data=await res.json();window.Common.showToast(data.message,!res.ok && res.status !==409);if(res.ok){watchlistLoaded=false;}};window.__portfolioExtrasLoaded=true;})();